                     <note type="general">Written along the fibers; on the back there is the address along the fibers</note>
                     <note type="general">17 lines of writing in a large hand which becomes faster and smaller at the bottom</note>
                     <note type="general">The letter was probably written personally by Tourbon, like P.Col. X 278</note>
